      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Jouni Uski</b>\n</p><p><b>Jouni Uski</b>,<br />\na Finnish chess and computer chess aficionado. He is tester, collector of <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">test-positions</a>, frequent poster in <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">computer chess forums</a>, and long term member in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, \nwith interests in all aspects of <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">chess engines</a>, <a href=\"/Tournaments_and_Matches\" title=\"Tournaments and Matches\">tournaments</a> and <a href=\"/Checkmate\" title=\"Checkmate\">mate solving</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. In 1996 he reported on the <a href=\"/Human_vs._Computer_Match_in_Finland,_1996\" title=\"Human vs. Computer Match in Finland, 1996\">Human vs. Computer Match in Finland, 1996</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1996_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1996 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6