ass=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 23, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=28381\">What does 32 bit engine really mean?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 29, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=29327\">Bob, please forget WAC testsuite in Crafty testing!!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 11, 1998&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a>, <a href=\"/Win_at_Chess\" title=\"Win at Chess\">WAC</a> </li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=29329\">And here is corrected ECM testsuite (15 wrong positions removed)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 11, 1998&#160;»  <a href=\"/Test-Positions\" title=\"Test-Positions\">Test-Positions</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=29328\">24 interesting endgame positions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 12, 1998</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=39972\">Here's the suite</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 18, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=45368\">Correction to Jouni's endgame test</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 08, 1999</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=57611\">WCCC and some NPS observations</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 23, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/WCCC_1999\" title=\"WCCC 1999\">WCCC 1999</a>, <a href=\"/Nodes_per_Second\" title=\"Nodes per Second\">Nodes per Second</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=58557\">What went wrong with P.Conners and Zugzwang in WCCC?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 29, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/WCCC_1999\" title=\"WCCC 1999\">WCCC 1999</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jouni_Uski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=121556\">About PConners</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/P.ConNerS\" title=\"P.ConNerS\">P.ConNerS</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=189107\">Big Book Of Combinations (long post)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 17, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=198429\">About diminishing returns (Uri)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 22, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Depth#DiminishingReturns\" title=\"Depth\">Diminishing Returns</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=249157\">what's this \"