ame\">Endgame</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27334\">What is perft(x) exactly meaning?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 06, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Perft\" title=\"Perft\">Perft</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jouni_Uski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36592\">Do You really need 1000s of games for testing?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 04, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37616\">Yet Another Mate Solving Test</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 14, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40289\">What makes 1-cpu program un-deterministic?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 06, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41414\">Beginner question about null-move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 11, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=45500&amp;start=2\">Re: WCCC Paderborn 1999</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 09, 2